OL,6,FA mother has been jailed for smuggling
OL,7,Faround #1m worth of drugs and phones
OL,8,Finto prisons across the UK.
OL,10,FLucy Adcock, 47, headed up a group who
OL,11,Forganised 22 drops in a month across
OL,12,Fsix British jails before she was
OL,13,Farrested in a Premier Inn car park in
OL,14,FBridgend, Merthyr Tydfil Crown Court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FThe group used drones to sneak the
OL,18,Fcontraband into jails, including the
OL,19,Ftroubled HMP Parc in Bridgend.
