OL,6,FProsecutor Matthew Cobbe said staff at
OL,7,FParc Prison found a dropped package on
OL,8,FApril 24 last year containing illicit
OL,9,Fitems worth #50,000 inside jails.
OL,10,FClass A and B drugs, as well as mobile
OL,11,Fphones were inside the package.
OL,13,FThe drone operator was not identified
OL,14,Fat this stage but two more packages
OL,15,Fwere recovered from the exercise yard
OL,16,Fat Parc the following month.
OL,18,FPolice were alerted and automatic
OL,19,Fnumber-plate recognition was used to
OL,20,Fidentify vehicles in the area at the
OL,21,Ftime.
