OL,6,F"It wasn't long before Lucy Adcock's
OL,7,Fcar was traced," said Mr Cobbe.
OL,9,F"She had driven down from the London
OL,10,Farea and she was stopped in the car
OL,11,Fpark of the Premier Inn in Bridgend by
OL,12,Fofficers later that day. She had a
OL,13,Fdrone in the car with her. In fact the
OL,14,Fdrone had software that could be
OL,15,Fdownloaded and examined.
