OL,6,F"The examination revealed that it had
OL,7,Fbeen used not just during the early
OL,8,Fhours of that morning to deliver drugs
OL,9,Fto Parc prison but it had been used on
OL,10,Fmany previous occasions and other
OL,11,Fprisons across the country."
OL,13,FIt was revealed that in the month
OL,14,Fleading up to May 11, the group had
OL,15,Fflown 22 drones over five other
OL,16,Fprisons - Gartree in Leicestershire,
OL,17,FOnley in Warwickshire, Guys Marsh in
OL,18,FShaftesbury, High Down in Sutton, and
OL,19,Fthe Mount in Hemel Hempstead.
