OL,6,FAnalysis of Adcock's phone led to
OL,7,Fpolice arresting four others who were
OL,8,Fpart of the scheme. Craig Davenport,
OL,9,FRyan Dorland, Nicola Ogle, and Emma
OL,10,FWatson all admitted involvement in the
OL,11,Fconspiracy.
OL,13,FMr Cobbe said the group attached
OL,14,Ffishhooks to the packages to make them
OL,15,Feasier to grab from inside a jail
OL,16,Fcell. A sheet would be thrown out to
OL,17,Fsnag onto the package and draw it in.
OL,19,FPackages recovered included cocaine,
OL,20,Fthe painkiller Phenacetin, cannabis
OL,21,Fresin, iPhones, sim cards and tobacco.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
