OL,6,FIt was estimated the group supplied
OL,7,Fitems with a total prison market value
OL,8,Fof #1,099,670 to #1,426,150.
OL,10,FThe prosecutor said Adcock "played the
OL,11,Fleading role both directing the others
OL,12,Fand taking a hands-on role".
OL,14,FAdcock, of Ruislip, London, Davenport,
OL,15,F46, of Clacton-on-Sea, Essex, and
OL,16,FDorland, 44, recently of HMP Brixton,
OL,17,Fwere sentenced on Monday after
OL,18,Fpleading guilty to a conspiracy to
OL,19,Fconvey A-list and B-list items into
OL,20,Fprison.
