OL,6,FHowever Dorland maintained he was not
OL,7,Faware there were Class A drugs among
OL,8,Fthe material that went over prison
OL,9,Fwalls.
OL,11,FJudge Paul Hobson jailed Adcock for
OL,12,Fsix years, Davenport for four years
OL,13,Fand nine months, and Dorland for four
OL,14,Fyears. Ogle and Watson are due to be
OL,15,Fsentenced at a later date.
